channel.description: Recent content in Services on Upshore Immigration Services

item.title: Express entry
item.description: Federal Express Entry program accepts applications under Federal Skilled Worker, Federal Skilled Trades and Canadian Experience class.

item.title: Visitor visa
item.description: Canada is a beautiful country with people of all cultures from around the world. Come as a visitor and fall in love!

item.title: Study permit
item.description: Come to study in Canada’s esteemed educational institutions. Many students go on to get work permits and become permanent residents.

item.title: Work permit
item.description: Work permits are granted under many categories such as LMIA based, LMIA exempted, NAFTA, Open, Post Graduate & Intra-company transferee.
